Inspired by:

http://blogs.atlassian.com/2013/03/instant-java-provisioning-with-vagrant-and-puppet-stash-one-click-install/

Installs Oracle java 8 including eclipse.

SSH X forwarding enabled, 
vagrant ssh and start eclipse with ./eclipse/eclipse

The /workspace directory on the host machine is a suitable place for your
eclipse workspace, have fun! You can then use commandline version control tools
to manager your commits.
